Package: compartmap
Type: Package
Title: A/B compartment inference from scRNA-seq, scATAC-seq and methylation array data
Description: Compartmap performs shrunken A/B compartment inference from scRNA-seq, scATAC-seq, scBS-seq, and methylation arrays.
